Uh. that's really far.

47
00:06:04.400 --> 00:06:07.900
Uh.

48
00:06:16.040 --> 00:06:19.540
that's not our sun.

49
00:06:21.480 --> 00:06:24.980
That's not our sun.

50
00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:41.340
Is the fuel.

51
00:07:19.810 --> 00:07:22.767
We are just minutes away from the fuel
station.

52
00:07:22.791 --> 00:07:24.801
We're going to fly by through the Petrova.

53
00:07:24.825 --> 00:07:28.006
Line near Venus. so what can
you tell us about the ArcLight probe?

54
00:07:28.030 --> 00:07:31.530
What do we expect to find?

55
